{"data":[{"date":"05:48 19/07","title":"Arsenal b\u1ecb l\u1eeba ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/arsenal-bi-lua-ngoan-muc-khi-ky-hop-dong-voi-cong-ty-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4361","checkdouble":"191555"},{"date":"06:59 19/07","title":"Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ea1t 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean Instagram","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/neymar-la-cau-thu-bong-da-thu-hai-dat-100-trieu-theo-doi-tren-instagram.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u00f3 th\u00eam 10 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u00f3 th\u00eam 10 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i h\u00f4m 16/7, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m C. Ronaldo (135 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i) trong nh\u00f3m V\u0110V. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 11 trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @instagram, Neymar l\u1ecdt top 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i do Facebook s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u00e0y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Instagram c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Instagram c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cc-3351-1531904636.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng con trai Davi Lucca tr\u00ean Instagram. \u1ea2nh: Instagram.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC. Ronaldo ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 5/2017. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 11 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i trong th\u1eddi gian World Cup di\u1ec5n ra, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng sau danh ca Selena Gomez (138 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i). Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau sao Messi \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay sau v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Neymar, v\u1edbi 97 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1edfi pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m trong \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00f2ng 1/8. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 pha tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\nAdvertisement<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ba ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n V\u0110V n\u00e0o g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong top 25. CLB th\u1ec3 thao duy nh\u1ea5t g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong top 25 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Instagram l\u00e0 Real Madrid, v\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4360","checkdouble":"191559"},{"date":"18:02 18/07","title":"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi Juve, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/insigne-canh-bao-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Napoli Insigne v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Serie A.</h2><h2>Ronaldo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u2018B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u2019 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Champions League.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Insigne tro lai\" title=\"Insigne tro lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/2/8/Nhung-ngoi-sao-co-the-thay-the-Coutinho-tai-Liverpool-hinh-anh-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Insigne c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Serie A</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd. Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Napoli Lorenzo Insigne cho hay: ''Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Italia, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u00f2 m\u00f2 mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Serie A. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Italy r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi anh \u1ea5y t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Juventus. H\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, Napoli c\u1ee7a Insigne c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a Juventus. V\u1edbi\u00a0vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Carlo Ancelotti l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm t\u1ea1i Serie A. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Insigne v\u00e0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span><br>\r\nCassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Rafael Nadal v\u00e0 Roger Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn-188-191518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn-188-191518.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u00e1n m\u1ecdi t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n \u1edf TBN</span><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Juventus mu\u1ed1n kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Italy.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\n100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo nghe t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4359","checkdouble":"191527"},{"date":"20:12 18/07","title":"Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>CLB Juventus s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Diego Godin\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/26/MU-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-Diego-Godin-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, Diego Godin ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay t\u1ea1i CLB Atletico Madrid trong su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 45 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Los Rojiblancos\u00a0v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay, CLB Juventus \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mang anh v\u1ec1 Turin. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Italy, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Diego Godin. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italy s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi m\u00e0 Juve \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 QBV 2017 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u201cr\u1ebb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u201d, kho\u1ea3ng 18 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng do trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Italia \u00a0sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay kh\u00f4ng?</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-yeu-to-chi-ra-ronaldo-nen-chon-mu-thay-vi-den-juventus-172-191429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-yeu-to-chi-ra-ronaldo-nen-chon-mu-thay-vi-den-juventus-172-191429.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra Ronaldo n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn M.U thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span><br>\r\nSau 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng CR7 n\u00ean v\u1ec1 M.U thay v\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\n100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo nghe t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4358","checkdouble":"191540"},{"date":"22:06 18/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo chia tay Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga, Javier Tebas cho r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp.\r\n</h2><h2>Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid v\u00ec thu\u1ebf\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chu-tich-La-Liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-Ronaldo-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 v\u00ec thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid sau 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u2018d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u2019 song m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga, Javier Tebas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa khi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn CR7 \u2018li h\u00f4n\u2019 Real l\u00e0 do li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1edd\u00a0Mundo Deportivo, \u00f4ng Tebas cho hay: \"Ronaldo ra \u0111i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf. \u1ede T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thu\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Italy. Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay gi\u1ea3i La Liga song kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tebas lo ng\u1ea1i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, t\u00f4i lo r\u1eb1ng La Liga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t 9 ho\u1eb7c 10 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thu\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 ho\u1eb7c 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 thu nh\u1eadp tr\u00ean 300 ngh\u00ecn euro/n\u0103m s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p 52% ti\u1ec1n thu\u1ebf. T\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m sau thu\u1ebf cho Ronaldo th\u00ec Los Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 57,7 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m cho CR7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ee9c thu\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Italia ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 43%.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span><br>\r\nCassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Rafael Nadal v\u00e0 Roger Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4357","checkdouble":"191544"},{"date":"23:33 18/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/3/4/da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t khi m\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Inte Milan quy\u1ebft gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi\u00a0ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Inter \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 khi anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi 44% t\u1ed5ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 Nerazzui c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Icardi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba chia tay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Ronaldo. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u2018ve v\u00e3n\u2019 c\u1ee7a Real, CLB Inter Milan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u2018tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u2019 Icardi. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Gazzetta dello Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd s\u1edbm g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 7,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 5,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i Serie A. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Icardi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus - Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Inter cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Inter t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7: Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale</span><br>\r\nReal ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale, Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic cho M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4356","checkdouble":"191546"},{"date":"19:15 18/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp c\u1ee7a VFF chi\u1ec1u 18/7, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Park.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Park chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp c\u1ee7a VFF chi\u1ec1u 18/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTrong vai tr\u00f2 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp. Do m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c n\u00ean UAE v\u00e0 Palestine ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, khi c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD\u201d, th\u1ea7y Park t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi. T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8 t\u1edbi 7/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu C\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-191477.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/19/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-191477.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br />\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4355","checkdouble":"191537"},{"date":"21:38 18/07","title":"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh do b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 thi\u00ean v\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/nhan-tai-khong-ngai-xuat-than.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ecb x\u1eed thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi thi\u00ean v\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi thi\u00ean v\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi thi\u00ean v\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/32512161_233763940726674_197930110387486720_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i do m\u1ea5t v\u00e9 l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn &lsquo;chung k\u1ebft&rsquo; gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u00ean ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2019, CLB B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u1ed1 Hi\u1ebfn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u l\u1eabn Ph\u1ed1 Hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean V\u0169ng T\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V\u0169ng T\u00e0u \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;truy \u0111u\u1ed5i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Nguy\u1ec5n Anh V\u0169 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0&nbsp;L\u00ea Tr\u1ea7n Ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 Hu\u1ef3nh Qu\u1ed1c Long \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh &lsquo;\u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7&rsquo;.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>R\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u, t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n an to\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a nguy\u00ean Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP HCM L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng Ti\u1ebfn, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb l\u00f2 SLNA, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c. V\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V\u0169ng T\u00e0u s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t th\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1eeb VFF.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/19/cau-thu-vung-tau-duoi-danh-trong-tai-1531913303.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4354","checkdouble":"191542"},{"date":"18:58 18/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7: Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale, Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic cho M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7.</h2><h2>Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng TBN, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Bale nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n: CLB Man United ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 cho Lukaku \u0111\u1ebfn Bernabeu theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eeba qua, Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 187 Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 187 Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/ngay-hom-nay-206.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>MU ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd Bale</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;h\u00e9t gi\u00e1&rsquo; ng\u00f4i sao Perisic c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro (62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a M.U. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro tuy nhi\u00ean sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng: Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh, CLB Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, AS Roma.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay (18/07), h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t trang tin uy t\u00edn nh\u01b0 Goal, The Telegraph \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker v\u1edbi AS Roma sau khi n\u00e2ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Hazard \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Real Madrid<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea cho th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi t\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho CLB l\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i hay kh\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Pogba mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 Juventus<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Tuttosport, Paul Pogba \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB, anh g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh 4 Scuddetto c\u00f9ng 2 Coppa Italia. H\u00e8 2016, M.U quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua l\u1ea1i anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 89,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Marca, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u1ec9 &nbsp;\u0111ang t\u00ecm mua nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n trung t\u00e2m luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Real v\u00e0 \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 \u1edf TBN \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo Marca, Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua Neymar v\u00e0o h\u00e8 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Paris th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<h2>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Le10 Sport cho hay, tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 PSG, Kante kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n hay \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Chelsea r\u1eb1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a The Blues.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\nXem th\u00eam:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-187-gang-tay-vang-world-cup-tien-sat-toi-real-184-191475.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7: &ldquo;G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng&rdquo; World Cup ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-van-de-can-mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819-172-191528.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-van-de-can-mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-van-de-can-mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819-172-191528.html\">3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong top 6. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t hay s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\"></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4353","checkdouble":"191536"},{"date":"06:35 19/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/07: MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-1907-mu-chi-130-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-cau-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 19/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1907 MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1907 MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-1907-MU-chi-130-trieu-bang-cho-2-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Chamberlain</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t khi m\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Unai Emery v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Godin\" title=\"trung ve Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Godin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot Malcom c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, Everton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom c\u1ee7a Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial Mourinho\" title=\"Martial Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/2/mourinho-quyet-tam-chan-duong-roi-old-trafford-cua-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester &ndash; V\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Martial \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Pjanic&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang-172-191553.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang-172-191553.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4352","checkdouble":"191558"},{"date":"21:51 18/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nou Camp nh\u1edd Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/tan-binh-barca-cap-ben-nou-camp-nho-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n binh v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp Barca, Arthur Melo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft l\u00fd do m\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb Neymar.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \">Arthur Melo t\u1edbi Barca nh\u1edd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Neymar</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, CLB Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Gremio. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng 21 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo t\u1edbi Barca nh\u1edd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo t\u1edbi Barca nh\u1edd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/arthur-phat-bieu-ngay-gia-nhap-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur&nbsp;c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nou Camp nh\u1edd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Neymar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arthur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ban b\u1eadt m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Barca, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Arthur \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn anh gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Khi t\u00f4i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Barca, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn tin cho t\u00f4i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 Barcelona. Anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t CLB tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ed1ng. N\u00f3i chung m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do ch\u1ecdn Barca, Arthur c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Nou Camp. T\u00e2n binh Barca cho hay: &quot;M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n, tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arthur s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 395,6 tri\u1ec7u euro khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7: Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale</span><br>\r\nReal ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale, Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic cho M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4351","checkdouble":"191543"},{"date":"04:53 19/07","title":"MU mu\u1ed1n \"\u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m\" Bayern Munich","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang The Independent \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago v\u00e0 Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean \u0111a n\u0103ng Dalot v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Fred.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong MU muon co Lewandowski va Thiago\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang The Independent \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho nh\u1eafm Thiago nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Carrick, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Barca v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lukaku \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm Lewandowski nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i. M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Khong de de MU co Lewandowski va Thiago\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/de.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 46 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Bayern ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, M.U c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Thiago \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Real trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Lewandowski trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Bayern Munich ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Thiago v\u00e0 110 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Lewandowski.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thiago v\u00e0 Lewandowski, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marko Arnautovic c\u1ee7a West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4350","checkdouble":"191550"},{"date":"05:18 19/07","title":"Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tru-cot.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chamberlain-chan-thuong-nghiem-trong-172-185032.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span>. C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 18 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Kolarov.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tru-cot.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chamberlain ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Chamberlain g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 Chamberlain s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Chamberlain g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Chamberlain\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Chamberlain \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chamberlain chan thuong va se phai nghi thi dau dai han\" title=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/klopp-van-mong-cho-dieu-ky-dieu-voi-chamberlain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Chamberlain \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Anfield v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChamberlain \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn, \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4349","checkdouble":"191551"}]}